              "name": "abtHeroSub",
              "fill": "$text-secondary",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 800,
              "content": "Traditional image editing outsourcing is built on black boxes, hidden fees, and slow communication. Reframe is the correction. We combined an AI-powered logistics layer with actual human masters of light and shadow.",
