                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "gcsxX",
                  "name": "abtVal1P",
                  "fill": "$text-secondary",
                  "content": "AI runs the workflow, but humans do the editing. We don't rely on generic filters or automated 'meh'. Every image is touched by an expert in-house editor who understands your brand's unique lighting and texture.",
